---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="/stack | MERULOX" description="Operational systems running in the background.">
	<h1>Stack</h1>

	<section class="work-list" aria-label="Stack">
		<article class="work-item">
			<header class="item-header">
				<h2>Brain / Memory System</h2>
				<span class="date">ongoing</span>
			</header>
			<p>
				Persistent knowledge graph fed by ingested content. Multiple Claude instances read
				from and write to a shared vault. Synthesis and promotion run on schedule.
			</p>
		</article>

		<article class="work-item">
			<header class="item-header">
				<h2>Outreach Pipeline</h2>
				<span class="date">2026</span>
			</header>
			<p>
				Lead scraping → SMS → reply agent → close agent. Twilio. Claude API. Python.
			</p>
		</article>

		<article class="work-item">
			<header class="item-header">
				<h2>Command Center</h2>
				<span class="date">running</span>
			</header>
			<p>Dashboard and Telegram commander. Monitors services, routes commands, surfaces signals.</p>
		</article>
	</section>
</Layout>
